name: Umak has Arrived in Blao
description:
Umak has arrived in a dystopian city called Blao. 
with his costume, he only bring his crap bucket to live and survive in the city of disillusionment.

the work is a tribute to @gogoporen #GOGO4HEN.
Made from photograph i took in South Bandung and composed (collaged) in photoshop to create visual narratifs.
